bgm.name: 魔王魂 ダンジョン22

parameters: 歩行紅
歩行紅

Regulus: "The surveillance mission at the academy will
continue with the current members. Sirius and AkeLunar,
please support Spica and Antares while carrying out your
duties."

\F[sirius_smile]Akane: "So it's decided that there will be no punishment
this time. That must mean the higher-ups are also feeling
the danger."

Regulus: "That is something you don't need to know. I will
provide as much support as possible. However, I feel that
the situation is becoming more than you can handle."

\F[sirius_angry]Akane: "Even though the codename Sirius is a proof of being
the strongest? Doesn't that mean there's nothing we can do
if it's beyond our control?"

Regulus: "You're as cheeky as ever. Very well. This time, I
will come over and help out myself."
\F[sirius_trouble]Akane: "Eh!? Th-that is..."

Regulus: "Is there a problem...? Please wait with bated
breath, Sirius."
\F[sirius_trouble]Akane: "Ugh..."
\FF[nakosu_smile]Nadeshiko: "What did Regulus say...?"

\FF[yurisu_smile]Yurika: "I've never met them either, the highest
authority... I'm curious..."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "...They're coming..."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Huh? What do you mean?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "They're going to come here directly. Ahh~! I have a
bad feeling about this~!"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "It seems like a sign that things are getting
serious. My arms are itching for action."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "It sounds like we should be gentle, but that's
not going to happen, is it?"

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "This is the worst! It just means more people to nag
us!"
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "But if it's the two of us, we can overcome it."
\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Hey hey. Don't forget about me."

\F[sirius_trouble]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "We're here too. We'll help out, even if only a
little."
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Everyone... Thank you!"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Let's protect this academy. From now on... forever
and ever! No matter what enemy comes, we won't lose!"
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Yeah...!"
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[yurisu_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Yes...!"
\F[sirius_smile]\FF[iruka_smile]\AA[2]Iruka: "Yes...!"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[inu_trouble]\AA[2]Anna Maple: "(...Is it okay to be so excited when Teacher
Achiri isn't here? If it's about the agent's duties... there
might be problems...?)"

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[inu_trouble]\AA[2]Anna Maple: "(Well, it feels like youth... I won't say
anything out of place. But, it does bother me...)"
A
